title: I Was Reincarnated but I Don’t Know Why - Novel Updates
tags: Adventurers   Depictions of Cruelty   Female Protagonist   Overpowered Protagonist   Protagonist Strong from the Start   R-15   Reincarnated in Another World   Sword And Magic   Time Skip
author: 紗凪 ケイ
description:
By the time I noticed, I was staring at the hands of a baby.

It seems like for some reason, I got myself reincarnated.

I also knew that I posses great power (Physical).

However, I was born in a really small peaceful village,

and there’s no place for me to demonstrate that power.

I’m also able to make friends with someone, but she was born with a sickly body…

I tried doing various things in order to grasp my power,

what I thought at that time was 『I want to go on an adventure freely』.

Incidentally, when went to the capital I raised a fuss, why won’t you let me do whatever I want?

And that’s where everything began.>
